    "latex": "\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{y}}{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_1}=\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_2}{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_1}\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_3}{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_2}\\frac{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_4}{\\partial \\mathbf{f}_3}\\qquad (11.3)"
